
Overview of adj sporty

The adj sporty has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. clean, sporting, sporty, sportsmanlike -- (exhibiting or calling for sportsmanship or fair play; "a clean fight"; "a sporting solution of the disagreement"; "sportsmanlike conduct")
2. flashy, gaudy, jazzy, showy, sporty -- ((used especially of clothes) marked by conspicuous display)
3. sporty -- (appropriate for sport or engagement in a sport)
